strings: <voice_0x010011D5><se_low>*: The doubts are coming and you have made good progress.
<voice_0x010011D6><se_low>*: ... Here it is all...! - We're on the mend! Ultimately!
<voice_0x010011D8><se_low>*: ...... Ha ha ha! If it were that easy, we could do so much more! Beginners don't even need to reach the top!
<voice_0x010011D9><se_low>*: good man! I'm Radon, what do you expect from such a sculptor?
<voice_0x010011DA><se_low>gain: ...I found a skeleton of a crane! Is it an old gem?
<voice_0x010011DB><se_low>gain: You left our family a few years ago. I have not met her yet.
<voice_0x010011DC><se_low>gain: I heard that one of my grandparents used it on me...open it! It is happening
<voice_0x010011DD><se_low>gain: shout at me I'm still skeptical on this!
<voice_0x010011DE><se_low>gain: However, I heard that one of my grandparents used it for carving.
<voice_0x010011DF><se_low>gain: Yes, he said it was the pinnacle of his career. your best job
<voice_0x010011E0><se_low>gain: Where are the statues now? Honestly, I don't know either. You have to check it out for yourself.
<voice_0x010011E1><se_low>gain: All I can say is the woman's name. If the old man didn't let me down, her name is Alexandra.
<voice_0x010011E2><se_low>gain: I'm sorry if I couldn't be of any help. out
<voice_0x010011E3><se_low>gain: What level! My son says he has to go and see him one day! Yes! Long time not seeing!
<voice_0x010011E4><se_low>gain: If a beginner like you can reach the top of my tower, it's all in my hands. We have to build higher! As they say<:> the only way up!
